---
title: Grilled Hoisin Tenderloin Steak Lettuce Wraps with Spicy Mayo and Peanut-Garlic Crisp
description: Easy enough for a weeknight dinner but special enough to prepare on the weekend for guests, lettuce wraps will be your new favourite summertime go-to. Lightly charred hoisin steak is thinly sliced and stacked with fragrant jasmine rice, quick pickles and a crackle topping you'll want to put on everything!
